_vrf_PLAT342_n2-MAPbI-C6-300K    
;
PROBLEM: Low Bond Precision on  C-C Bonds ...............      0.072 Ang.  
RESPONSE:  The crystal quality became worse due to the phase change and/or 
 X-ray damage. The organic cations were located in difference-Fourier maps. 
 The restraints on bond lengths of the atomic displacement parameters 
 (DFIX/SADI instructions of SHELXL-2014), as well as the constraints or 
 restraints of the atomic displacement parameters (RIGU or SIMU/ISOR 
 instructions of SHELXL-2014) if necessary, have been applied for 
 organic cations refinement. 
;
